I guess they got it wrong here, shouldn't this be Naina barse and man tarse?.......lol
Also, "yaad tainoon kerna" part is tune taken from famous folk song "Baari thaani charhya" by Tassavur Khanum and it is just beautiful.
Right after listening to Fakhir I could tell I have heard this tune when I was a kid so I searched and found it. Our music heritage is simply brilliant and matchless.
